Feature: Nykaa Shopping Cart 
	As a shopper, I want to add products to my cart and proceed to checkout.
  
Scenario: order a item 

	Given user can launch the url																
	When user can go to the skin tab 
	And user can go to select skin wash
	Then user will be able to successsfully  switch to facewash tab
	
Scenario:  add the product in cart 
	Given user can select the prefered face wash 
	When  user can select the shade of the face wash
	And  user can add the product to the bag 
	Then user can noe see the product in the cart